# POC Dating Application - Git Ignore Rules
#
# PURPOSE: Prevents committing sensitive/generated files to version control
#
# WHY THIS APPROACH:
# - Keeps secrets out of git history
# - Prevents IDE/build artifacts from cluttering repo
# - Reduces repository size and improves performance
#
# ORGANIZATION:
# - IDE-specific patterns first
# - Build/compile artifacts
# - Dependencies
# - Environment/config files
# - OS-specific files

# ========================================
# IDE & EDITOR CONFIGURATION
# ========================================

# JetBrains IDEs (IntelliJ, WebStorm, PhpStorm, RubyMine, AppCode, CLion, etc.)
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
*.ipr
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Visual Studio Code
.vscode/
*.code-workspace

# Sublime Text
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# Vim
.vim/
[._]*.s[a-w][a-z]
[._]s[a-w][a-z]

# Emacs
*~
\#*\#
.\#*

# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*

# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

